Spread the love of Lingokids with cool stickers for kids. These fun stickers
bring Cowy, Billy, Lisa, Elliot, and Baby Bot to life!

Please Note: Custom fees may apply depending on the territory.

Don't forget to clean the surface before applying the stickers

  
• Film type: MPI 3000 Gloss HOP (EU), Promotional Monomeric PVC (US)  
• 0.12″ (0.3 cm) white sticker border  
• Glossy finish  
• Fast and easy application  
• 2–3 year durability  
• Indoor use  
• Blank product sourced from Japan
